# {{ project_name }}

A presentation project created with [Aurea](https://github.com/aurea/aurea).

## Quick Start

Your project is set up for **{{ agent }}** with the **{{ theme }}** theme.

### Workflow (7 phases)

```
/aurea.theme    → Browse and select a theme
/aurea.outline  → Generate narrative structure and slide plan
/aurea.generate → Create full Markdown presentation
/aurea.refine   → Improve specific slides (usage: /aurea.refine <feedback>)
/aurea.visual   → Generate SVG/CSS visual assets
/aurea.extract  → Extract a design system from a URL
/aurea.build    → Build the standalone HTML presentation
```

Start here: `/aurea.outline "{{ project_name }}"`

### CLI Commands

```bash
# Build the presentation
aurea build

# Preview locally
aurea serve

# Browse themes
aurea theme list
aurea theme search "dark minimal"

# Apply a different theme
aurea theme use midnight

# Watch mode (rebuild on save)
aurea build --watch
```

### Project Structure

```
{{ project_name }}/
├── .aurea/
│   ├── config.json          # Project configuration
│   └── themes/              # Local theme files
├── slides/
│   └── presentation.md      # Your Markdown slides
├── output/
│   └── presentation.html    # Generated HTML (offline-ready)
└── README.md
```

### Slide Format

```markdown
---
title: "My Presentation"
author: "Your Name"
theme: "{{ theme }}"
---

# Slide Title

Slide content goes here (≤40 words)

Note: Speaker notes go here. Rich detail, context, talking points.

---

## Next Slide

- Bullet point 1
- Bullet point 2

Note: More speaker notes.
```

Separate slides with `---` on a line by itself.
